text: KQNY (91.9 FM) is a radio station licensed to serve the community of Quincy, California. The station is owned by Plumas Community Radio and airs a variety format. The station was assigned the KQNY call letters by the Federal Communications Commission on October 17, 2008. ==References== ==External links== * Official Website * QNY Category:Radio stations established in 2010 Category:2010 establishments in California Category:Variety radio stations in the United States Category:Community radio stations in the United States Category:Plumas County, California
